### README

All-in-one scripts (see INSTALL-debian-nginx-phpfpm-aegir.sh.txt)
to install ready to use Aegir Hosting System for Drupal.


### REQUIREMENTS

* Debian 5.0 Lenny minimal (base) OS fresh install (Ubuntu version soon).


### PROVIDES

* All libraries & tools required to install and run Nginx based Aegir system.
* Latest MariaDB database server.
* Nginx 0.8.46 web server with upload progress and Boost support.
* PHP-FPM 5.2.13 with APC, memcache, uploadprogress and suhosin.
* Maintenance & Auto-Healing scripts in /var/xdrago.
* Automated daily backups for all databases in /data/disk/arch/sql.


### HELP

* See: http://groups.drupal.org/nginx


### MAINTAINERS

